[normal]Responses to specific questions raised are as follows:-
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Why do numbers of women in STEM academic careers decline further up the career ladder? 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]When women leave academia, what careers do they transition into? What are the consequences of scientifically trained women applying their skills in different 
[normal]employment sectors?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]What should 
[normal]universities and the higher education sector do to retain women graduates and PhD students in academic careers? Are there examples of good practice?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]What role should the Government have in encouraging the retention of women in academic STEM careers?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
